abstract: JPMorgan Asset Management has raised $600 million for its Greater China Property Fund. The closed-end JPMorgan Greater China Property Fund received capital commitments from institutional and high-net-worth investors from the U.S., Asia, Europe and the Middle East.

headline.main: JPMorgan Raises $600 Million for China Property Fund
